episodes.title: Are You in a Christian Cult?
episodes.description:
In this video, I dive into the topic of dysfunctional Christian churches or cults, how to recognize the signs of a Christian cult, and what to prepare for if you decide to break free from dysfunctional teachings or unhealthy religious environments. I talk about the book Becoming Free Indeed by Jinger Duggar Vuolo and offer encouragement for those who are questioning the things they're being taught without completely deconstructing their faith.
